i ba b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Liverpool 3-0 Man City n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 m\u00f2n m\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexander-Arnold moi la nguoi hung tran Liverpool 3-0 Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Alexander-Arnold m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/khong-phai-salah-day-moi-la-nguoi-hung-thuc-su-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Alexander-Arnold t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f2n ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Mohamed Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 mang v\u1ec1 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch Etihad. Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Frank Lampard l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea: \u201cTheo t\u00f4i, Trent Alexander-Arnold m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi l\u00e0m sao khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 Champions League.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 coi th\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o gi\u1eef v\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c b\u1eaft ch\u1ebft Leroy Sane \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh. 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta ng\u1ee1 t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang xem m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</span></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"878","checkdouble":"183736"},{"date":"20:42 07/04","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn HLV Mihail chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/23/he-lo-ly-do-thuc-su-khien-hlv-mihail-chia-tay-flc-thanh-hoa.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-fam