 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n. Ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Everton \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, trong khi Liverpool tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Cho d\u00f9 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1edd h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng The Kop v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park, khi Bolasie tung c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, khi\u1ebfn Karius r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng trong hi\u1ec7p 2, tr\u1eadn derby s\u1ebd h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside gi\u1eefa Everton vs Liverpool di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n t\u1ebb\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n t\u1ebb\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/ever.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside gi\u1eefa Everton vs Liverpool di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n t\u1ebb</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede n\u1eeda sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 1, khi Everton vs Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u qu\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng. T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Jurgen Klopp, \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, b\u1edfi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 cho th\u1ea5y \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City \u1edf Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_265747\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/04/07/highlight-everton-vs-liverpool-vong-33-nha.mp4&amp;autoplay=false\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"873","checkdouble":"183730"},{"date":"18:56 07/04","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00f2ng 33 Premier League 2017/18 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 7/4","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/media