g\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau Bruna Marquezine kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh y\u00eau n\u1ed3ng th\u1eafm khi \u0111i xem k\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Brazil.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 t\u1edbi nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t Laura Alvin \u1edf Rio De Janeiro xem v\u1edf k\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a t\u00e1c gi\u00e0 Thiago Gagliasso h\u00f4m 5/4. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u00f4m eo ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Bruna Marquezine, k\u00e9o nghi\u00eang ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f4n, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ng\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh c\u00e1c paparazzi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ngoi sao Neymar cong khai hon ban gai trong rap hat hinh anh\" title=\"Ng\u00f4i sao Neymar c\u00f4ng khai h\u00f4n b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i trong r\u1ea1p h\u00e1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/7/neymar1a-1952-1523068813.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar v\u00e0 Bruna Marquezine tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh y\u00eau trong r\u1ea1p h\u00e1t. \u1ea2nh: Sun.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p d\u1ecbp cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Neymar v\u00e0 n\u1eef di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u1ea5n qu\u00fdt kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi. Trong 5 n\u0103m y\u00eau nhau, \u0111\u00f4i tr\u1ebb chia tay r\u1ed3i quay l\u1ea1i ba l\u1ea7n, sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c l\u1ea1i th\u1eafm thi\u1ebft h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y Neymar b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng hai, Bruna Marquezine lu\u00f4n \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh b\u1ea1n trai khi anh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Rio de Janeiro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Sun cho bi\u1ebft, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 World Cup \u1edf Nga v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 6 t\u1edbi. Neymar kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a PSG t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng hai t\u1edbi nay v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Brazil v\u00ec b\u1ecb bong g\u00e2n m\u1eaft c\u00e1, r\u1ea1n x\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n, ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eeba m\u1edbi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 198 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3n s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"867","checkdouble":"183723"},{"date":"10:39 07/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benevento vs Juventus 20h00 ng\u00e0y 7/4 (Serie A 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/nhan-dinh-benevento-vs-juventus-20h00-ngay-74-serie-a-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:lef