      <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Benevento vs Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benevento vs Juventus: 1-3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus \u0111ang \u1edf trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Benevento t\u1ed1i nay l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng hi\u1ebfm hoi, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Juve ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Sampdoria, Napoli, Inter v\u00e0 Roma. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Massimiliano Allegri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua Real Madrid 0-3 t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Juve \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u xem nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tin vui cho Serie A, b\u1edfi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf Bianconeri s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Benevento \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Juventus. L\u00e3o phu nh\u00e2n b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong n\u1eeda sau c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 2. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00f3t b\u1ea3ng, k\u00e9m 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n cho th\u1ea5y Benevento c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Juve t\u1ed1i nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb6C BI\u1ec6T<br>\r\nJuventus th\u1eafng v\u00e0 s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Serie A v\u00e0 Coppa Italia, Juventus th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 15/18 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Benevento l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu, Juve s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n<br></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"866","checkdouble":"183698"},{"date":"10:51 07/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Fiorentina 23h00 ng\u00e0y 7/4 (Serie A 2017/18)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/7/nhan-dinh-roma-vs-fiorentina-23h00-ngay-74-serie-a-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointe